To install

-- download npm

  npm install
  npm run buildgame

In browser load game.html.

This teaches a few basics in design.

 card-lib.js starts with basic object orientated design in JavaScript
 Uses jquery and jquery-ui libraries that are powerful UX framework for JS.

 How to play
   Make 3 or 4 of a kind (e.g ace,ace,ace)
   Make 3 in a row of same suite (e.g 9, 10, jack)

Aim is to turn this into a multi player game, where the state is handled by a
little server.
